{"tid":1834102,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"阿薩斯為防疫而屠城斯塔索姆其實好正確","createTime":"2020-01-22T09:00:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T05:04:30.000Z","uid":117332,"like":57,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"3dabfa9f9bb51e1f7e5383fc96ce1b4dbbdc25b5","tid":1834102,"uid":117332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T09:00:17.000Z","msg":"<em><span style=\"font-size: small;\">當時阿薩斯知道咗受瘟疫感染既糧食已經送去斯塔索姆。阿薩斯不顧眾人反對，堅持殺光城內所有居民百姓，以免佢哋在被瘟疫感染死後復活成喪屍。<br />\n<br />\n事後好多人認為阿薩斯既屠城無謀之舉，係眾多選項中都係較差既選擇。或者認為阿薩斯只係為咗盡早去北境先屠城節省兵力時間。</span></em><br />\n<br />\n其實而家諗番，王子屠城係正確的，如果唔係斯塔索姆既人就好可能會千方百計咁出逃，向其他人族領地輸出瘟疫，而且一定唔會自行報備而會千方百計隱瞞。<br />\n<br />\n同埋受感染糧食，一定唔會銷毀，而會被人用低價用淘寶賣走。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21859ae3617a1b767cc6b415dd1ac8fe284cf8c9","tid":1834102,"uid":5475,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T09:02:12.000Z","msg":"屠左咪又係有成堆食屍鬼出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ea303f9f3127fe11d30cd4b7d9b804409d971cc","tid":1834102,"uid":117332,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"21859ae3617a1b767cc6b415dd1ac8fe284cf8c9","tid":1834102,"uid":5475,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T09:02:12.000Z","msg":"屠左咪又係有成堆食屍鬼出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T09:04:45.000Z","msg":"起碼啲瘟疫唔會去其他地區先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過照計佢應該會賣去獸人國，或者係獸人既公屋樓下到派街坊先係。"},{"pid":"1c313358536d820e10b7bf2f81226a1e24e43da6","tid":1834102,"uid":55010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3dabfa9f9bb51e1f7e5383f